TUBE TALK Rib-ticklers

 The cast of Becker: Say cheese 

 Becker 

 John Becker (played by Ted Danson) is a doctor with a heart of gold but a big mouth. His staff suffers him for his helpful nature and his patients have learnt with his acerbic one-liners. But for his head nurse Margret, his clinic would have turned into a coop. Reggie, the attractive owner of the hotel where he dines has ?something? for him but she is quite confused. 

 Catch it on: Star World on Mondays at 9.30 pm

 Success story: Female viewers are known to fall for this loud-mouthed physician, very much like his patients of the opposite?and sometimes of the same?sex.

Ashton Kutcher 

 That ?70s show

 Rewind to the era of bell-bottoms and Elvis Presley, side locks and hard rock. Smoking pot was in vogue and breaking the rules was a norm. This is a story of a group of teenagers and their comic conflicts with their elders over issues like alcohol consumption and sex before marriage. 

 Catch it on: Star World on Mondays at 8 pm

 Success story: The characters are cool and their antics funny. The biggest USP is the milieu which transports you to the seventies.




